        {
            "title": "A股半日揚升   人大開幕利好",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股大幅反彈，深股升逾1%，兩市成交合計15478.37億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人大會議今早開幕，疊加外圍股市反彈，內地股市回升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指半日升34點或0.84%，報4116點，今早以4109點開市，升27點或0.67%，最低見4090，升8點或0.2%，兩會宣讀工作報告期間升幅擴大，最高見4123點，升41點或1%，半日成交6822.15億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指半日升232點或1.67%，報14150點，今早開市已重越14000點，開報14160點，升242點或1.74%，最低報14059，升142點或1.02%，中段見14202，升285點或2.05%，為半日高位，半日成交8656.22億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數半日升60點或1.31%，報4662，今早開升49點或1.07%，開報4651點；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數半日報3241，升76點或2.43%，今早開市報3236點，升71點或2.27%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15708827-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%8f%9a%e5%8d%87-%e4%ba%ba%e5%a4%a7%e9%96%8b%e5%b9%95%e5%88%a9%e5%a5%bd",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_ASHARE_5_source-ap_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 11:48:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全國兩會｜著力穩定房地產市場　優化保障性住房供給",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國務院總理李強發表政府工作報告，指出要著力穩定房地產市場，因城施策控增量、去庫存、優供給。深化住房公積金制度改革。優化保障性住房供給，加快危舊房改造，有序推動安全舒適綠色智慧「好房子」建設，實施房屋品質提升工程及物業服務質量提升行動，進一步發揮「保交房」白名單制度作用，防範債務違約風險。深入推進房地產發展新模式基礎制度及配套政策建設。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">報告又提到，積極有序化解地方政府債務風險。支持各地用足用好政策，加快化解隱性債務風險，嚴防虛假化債，堅決把遏制違規新增隱性債務作為鐵的紀律。積極穩妥化解金融領域風險。充實地方中小金融機構風險處置資源及手段。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15708919-%e5%85%a8%e5%9c%8b%e5%85%a9%e6%9c%83%ef%bd%9c%e8%91%97%e5%8a%9b%e7%a9%a9%e5%ae%9a%e6%88%bf%e5%9c%b0%e7%94%a2%e5%b8%82%e5%a0%b4%e3%80%80%e5%84%aa%e5%8c%96%e4%bf%9d%e9%9a%9c%e6%80%a7%e4%bd%8f%e6%88%bf-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230724_FI_source_licensed_China-Property_shutterstock-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 11:48:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "阿里巴巴吳泳銘發內部郵件證實林俊暘離職 明言將持續加大AI研發與吸納優秀人才",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地媒體報道，阿里巴巴(09988)首席執行官吳泳銘今早發出內部郵件，證實千問前負責人林俊暘離職，又指會持續加大AI研發與吸納優秀人才力度。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"吳泳銘 (圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241118_FI_source-web_09988.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"吳泳銘 (圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241118_FI_source-web_09988.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">吳泳銘 (圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">吳泳銘在發給通義實驗室人員的內部郵件中，表示公司已決定批准林俊暘辭職，感謝對方過去在崗位上的付出。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">他又指出，通義實驗室負責人周靖人會繼續帶領通義實驗室推進後續工作，公司將成立基礎模型支持小組，由吳泳銘本人、周靖人、范禹(吳澤明花名)共同協調集團資源支持基礎莫型建設。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">吳泳銘在郵件中又說，技術發展不進則退，發展基礎大模型是集團面向未來的關鍵戰略，集團將在繼續堅持開源模型策略的同時，持續加大對AI領域的研發投入，加人吸納優秀人才的力度。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15708720-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e5%90%b3%e6%b3%b3%e9%8a%98%e7%99%bc%e5%85%a7%e9%83%a8%e9%83%b5%e4%bb%b6%e8%ad%89%e5%af%a6%e6%9e%97%e4%bf%8a%e6%9a%98%e9%9b%a2%e8%81%b7-%e6%98%8e%e8%a8%80%e5%b0%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 11:14:43",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股早市反覆向上 升幅暫擴大至逾400點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股今早跟隨外圍高開後反覆向上，截至上午約10時49分，恒生指數升幅擴大至453點或1.8%，報25703點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指今早亦非無波動，於上午約10時曾回順至25490點，將升幅收窄至240點；早前高位25704點，升454點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數略為跑輸，暫升1.15%，報4885點。金融與地產股領漲，滙控(00005)升逾4%，友邦(01299)更漲超過5%；九龍倉置業(01997)亦升逾4.5%，新地(00016)升逾3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">機電設備股持續強勢，東方電機(01072)與上海電氣(02727)均飆逾16%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15708646-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e5%8f%8d%e8%a6%86%e5%90%91%e4%b8%8a-%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e6%9a%ab%e6%93%b4%e5%a4%a7%e8%87%b3%e9%80%be400%e9%bb%9e",
